`if we take piles[i][j] coin we need to take all the coins above index j in that i pile.`

`from above we can conlude that instead of taking one by one coin from a given row we take in bunch`

# Approach

`TRY ALL POSSIBLE WAYS`

`To take bunch of coins we used presum of all indivisual piles of coins`
