I kept 3 variables for a state ,
Index_of_pile --> which pile am i currently standing at  --> [i]
index_in_current_pile  --> which index is at the top at the moment for piles[index], -->  [j]
No_of_purchaces_remaining  ---> how many transactions do I have left with me ---> [k]

Dp[i][j][k] = returns me the maximum money i can retreive from here 
at this state i have 2 choices 
take the jth coin (topmost coin) on pile i  and stay on the same pile
dont take the jth coin and move the next pile

take : piles[i][j] + func(i , j + 1 , k - 1)
dont take : func(i + 1 , 0 , k - 1 ) --> 0 because now 0 is the topmost coin of the new pile

