# Approach
Create the method
```
private int MaxValueOfCoins((int index, int k) key, Dictionary<(int index, int k), int> dic, IList<IList<int>> piles)
```
, where
- (int index, int k) key contains the index of a current pile and k - the number of coins
- Dictionary<(int index, int k), int> dic is a dictionary with a result for a certain key
- IList<IList<int>> piles is an initial piles
Call this method recursively.
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
$$O(sum(len(piles[i])))$$

- Space complexity:
$$O(sum(len(piles[i])))$$

